These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, cooking, rock-climbing, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person who's hobby is sudoku##2
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |  2   |  3   |   4   |
| Hobby   | skydiving | sudoku | cooking | rock-climbing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: poker, bridge, backgammon, chess
1. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing poker##1
3. the person playing chess is between the person playing bridge and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |  3   |    4     |
| Game   | bridge | chess | poker | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-3::.
House: modern, farmhouse, cape-cod, craftsman
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the modern house##1
2. the cape-cod house is between the farmhouse house and the craftsman house##2
3. the modern house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |  3   |   4    |
| House   | modern | craftsman | cape-cod | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, musical, mystery, crime
1. the person watching mystery movies is between the person watching musical movies and the person watching thriller movies##2
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | musical | mystery | thriller |

